ption="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tiktok-evidence-e1691437478249.png" data-large-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tiktok-evidence-e1691437478249.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tiktok-evidence-e1691437478249.png" alt="" width="558" height="1047" class="alignright size-full wp-image-71841" style="max-width:300px" srcset="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tiktok-evidence-e1691437478249.png 558w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tiktok-evidence-e1691437478249-210x394.png 210w" sizes="(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px" /></a>一名女子的 TikTok 视频上不断有网络喷子发表评论，<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@rx0rcist/video/7251438901426965806">她通过一些公开信息猜出了他是谁</a>。</p><p>通过追踪数字足迹来寻找某些东西的侦探视频类型继续令人着迷。另外，这个真的很令人满意。尽管这也让我对隐私和人们利用这些信息来做坏事感到好奇。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/privacy/" rel="tag">隐私</a>, <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/tiktok/" rel="tag">TikTok</a> ,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/trolls/" rel="tag">巨魔</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 71824</post-id></item><item><title>将食谱保存到您的电子邮件</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2023/08/04/save-recipes-to-your-email/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Fri, 04 Aug 2023 18:21:11 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Data Sharing]]></category><category><![CDATA[Matthew Phillips]]></category><category><![CDATA[recipes]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=71820 </guid><description><![CDATA[Yums, by Matthew Phillips, is a quick and simple way to save recipes&#8230;<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/matthew-phillips/" rel="tag">马修·菲利普斯</a>，<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/recipes/" rel="tag">食谱</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> Matthew Phillips 的 Yums<a href="https://yums.email">是一种通过电子邮件保存食谱的快速而简单的方法</a>：</p><blockquote><p> Yums 是一个建立在电子邮件之上的菜谱存储系统。网络上的内容会随着时间的推移而消失，但电子邮件您可以永远控制。</p><p>要使用 Yums，请找到您喜欢的食谱，然后发送电子邮件至 save@yums.email。在正文中粘贴您要保存的食谱的链接。您可以粘贴任意多个链接，并用新行分隔。</p></blockquote><p>超级简单，电子邮件只是没有背景故事的食谱。我理解为什么人们在实际食谱之前添加所有文字和图片，但它已经失控了。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/matthew-phillips/" rel="tag">马修·菲利普斯</a>，<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/recipes/" rel="tag">食谱</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 71820</post-id></item><item><title> date-me 文档目录</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2023/08/04/directory-of-date-me-docs/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Fri, 04 Aug 2023 16:03:48 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Data Sharing]]></category><category><![CDATA[Date Me Doc]]></category><category><![CDATA[dating]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=71816 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2023/08/04/directory-of-date-me-docs/"><img width="750" height="472" src="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Date-Me-Docs-directory-750x472.png" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Date-Me-Docs-directory-750x472.png 750w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Date-Me-Docs-directory-1090x686.png 1090w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Date-Me-Docs-directory-210x132.png 210w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Date-Me-Docs-directory-768x484.png 768w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Date-Me-Docs-directory-1536x967.png 1536w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Date-Me-Docs-directory-2048x1290.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-attachment-id="71817" data-permalink="https://flowingdata.com/2023/08/04/directory-of-date-me-docs/date-me-docs-directory/" data-orig-file="https://flowingdata.